"A.P.238/4/9/10:55": "What are you doing by yourself? You know the rules of the tournament."
"You have to join in. If you go in alone you'll be disqualified."
"...Or did you not have anyone to invite?"
"...Sorry, I didn't mean anything by that! I just thought you'd be in demand for this...!"
"I guess there's no choice. Alright, I'll go with you. I wasn't busy anyway."
"So what am I doing here? That's none of your business. Would you rather I leave?"
